            <li><strong>If CAC = 0:</strong> Get metabolic panel with insulin</li>
            <li><strong>If family history:</strong> Add advanced lipids</li>
            <li><strong>Retest:</strong> CAC every 5 years if zero</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="action-box">
