        <ol>
            <li><strong>Get all tests:</strong> Don't wait</li>
            <li><strong>CAC score:</strong> Immediately</li>
            <li><strong>Full panels:</strong> Metabolic + inflammatory + advanced lipids</li>
            <li><strong>Track:</strong> Every 1-2 years</li>
